## Update User Password

#### **Authorization** \- ADMIN

This endpoint allows the user to update their password.

### Request Body

- `username` (string): The email address of the user.

- `password` (string): The new password for the user account.


### Response

The response is in plain text format and indicates the success of the password update operation.

``` json
{
  "type": "object",
  "properties": {
    "status": {
      "type": "number",
      "description": "The HTTP status code of the response."
    },
    "Content-Type": {
      "type": "string",
      "description": "The type of content in the response."
    },
    "message": {
      "type": "string",
      "description": "A message indicating the result of the password update operation."
    }
  }
}

 ```

## Send Request

This endpoint is used to send a request with a payload to the server.

### Request Body

- `branch`: (string) The branch related to the request.

- `message`: (string) The message for the request.


### Response

The response for this request will follow the JSON schema below:

``` json
{
  "type": "object",
  "properties": {
    "status": {
      "type": "string"
    },
    "timestamp": {
      "type": "string",
      "format": "date-time"
    }
  }
}

 ```

